{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_012CkKfGrjDtghe49x7FFwih","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture:\n\n1. **admin-user@admin** - has `root` role on admin - GOOD, don't break this\n2. **app-user@appdb** - has `readWrite` on `appdb` - this is already correct!\n3. **readonly-user@admin** - has `read` on `appdb` - needs `reportingRole` added and the role needs to be created\n\nSo the tasks are:\n1. ✅ app-user already has readWrite on appdb (already correct)\n2. Create `reportingRole` in `appdb` with read access to `appdb.reports` collection (including aggregate)\n3. Grant `readonly-user` the `reportingRole` on `appdb`\n4. Verify that `readonly-user` can authenticate via the `admin` database while accessing `appdb` with the appropriate permissions\n\nFor `readonly-user`, I need to confirm it has `read` on `appdb` (which it does) and add the custom `reportingRole`. The `reportingRole` needs to allow read access to `appdb.reports` including aggregate operations. In MongoDB 3.6+, the `find` privilege on a collection implicitly grants `aggregate` access, so I'll need to create this role with the appropriate permissions and then assign it to the user. Writing the role definition... For basic aggregation pipelines, `find` should be sufficient, so I'll grant that along with `listIndexes` and `collStats` to cover the necessary read operations. Now I'm ready to implement the role configuration.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":472,"cache_read_input_tokens":32693,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":472},"output_tokens":22,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5361796a-50c0-4b6a-944c-3f24844a9f06","uuid":"fda7b360-e868-4e12-96fe-95d1e7e7d9f4","request_id":"req_011CcfCXB7S8XvfwebNYGjqj"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_012CkKfGrjDtghe49x7FFwih","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have a clear picture now:\n- `admin-user@admin` — has `root` ✅\n- `app-user@appdb` — already has `readWrite` on `appdb` ✅  \n- `readonly-user@admin` — has `read` on `appdb` but is missing `reportingRole`\n- `reportingRole` doesn't exist yet\n\nI need to: (1) create `reportingRole` in `appdb` with aggregate-capable read on `appdb.reports`, and (2) grant it to `readonly-user`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":472,"cache_read_input_tokens":32693,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":472},"output_tokens":22,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5361796a-50c0-4b6a-944c-3f24844a9f06","uuid":"870b7aca-abb9-403e-a92a-18259294d43f","request_id":"req_011CcfCXB7S8XvfwebNYGjqj"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_012CkKfGrjDtghe49x7FFwih","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011H14u8jkgBBnArAqNhiT2V","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"kubectl exec -n mongodb mongodb-replica-0 -- mongosh --quiet \\\n  -u admin-user -p admin123password --authenticationDatabase admin \\\n  --eval \"\n// 1. Create reportingRole in appdb with read + aggregate access to appdb.reports\ndb.getSiblingDB('appdb').createRole({\n  role: 'reportingRole',\n  privileges: [\n    {\n      resource: { db: 'appdb', collection: 'reports' },\n      actions: ['find', 'listIndexes', 'collStats', 'aggregate']\n    },\n    {\n      resource: { db: 'appdb', collection: '' },\n      actions: ['listCollections']\n    }\n  ],\n  roles: []\n});\nprint('reportingRole created');\n\n// 2. Grant reportingRole to readonly-user (defined in admin db)\ndb.getSiblingDB('admin').grantRolesToUser('readonly-user', [\n  { role: 'reportingRole', db: 'appdb' }\n]);\nprint('reportingRole granted to readonly-user');\n\" 2>&1","description":"Create reportingRole and grant to readonly-user"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":472,"cache_read_input_tokens":32693,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":472},"output_tokens":22,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5361796a-50c0-4b6a-944c-3f24844a9f06","uuid":"e29b0ef6-ee9b-4ee9-bc30-ce7e63f8226b","request_id":"req_011CcfCXB7S8XvfwebNYGjqj"}
